article.description: Kendric Davis had 21 points as SMU edged past UNLV 72-68 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Davis scores 21 to lead SMU past UNLV 72-68
article.linkText: Davis scores 21 to lead SMU past UNLV 72-68
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- Kendric Davis had 21 points as SMU edged past UNLV 72-68 on Saturday night. Feron Hunt had 19 points for SMU (5-0). Isiaha Mike added 14 points and Tyson Jolly had seven assists for the Mustangs. Bryce Hamilton had 18 points for the Runnin' Rebels (2-5). Donnie Tillman and Amauri Hardy added 13 points apiece. SMU plays Hartford at home on Wednesday. UNLV matches up against Jackson State at home on Tuesday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
